headline: Ready, Set, Egg! Reese's and Cadbury Partner with Jasmine Roth to Kick Off a Fun New Easter Tradition
summary: Forget everything you thought you knew about "egging." This Easter, Reese's and Cadbury are flipping the script, turning an age-old prank into a revived tradition that's all about fun, surprises, and—of course—chocolate.
